    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, it runs well overall, but it may require some minor maintenance soon, such as a brake service or a tune-up, to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at an affordable price point who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
