    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in exceptional, showroom-quality condition. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining a deep, mirror-like finish with no scratches or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Every feature functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained to ensure it looks and drives as if it just left the dealership. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in truly mint condition.",
