    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration pros! This car is the ultimate project vehicle, offering a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to bring a machine back to life. While it's currently in poor condition and will need some serious TLC, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way to get your hands on a classic frame or valuable parts. Roll up your sleeves and get ready to create something special with this diamond in the rough!",
      "price": 3500.0,
